alerts.headline: Heavy Heat Stress
alerts.description: update: Severe Warning of HEAVY HEAT STRESS in Southern Golan, in Lower Galilee, in Bet Shean Valley, in Hula Valley, in Izrael Valley, in North Coast, in Centeral and South Coast, in Judean Foothills, in Northern Negev, in Eastern Negev, in Southern Negev and in Arava on 21/08 from 12 until 18 LT. For further details: https://ims.gov.il/he/IMSwarnings.
